0on%20small%20projects%2C%20under%201500%20records%20in%20each%20table.%0A%09%09%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%09%3Cdiv%3E%0A%09%09%3Ch3%3E%20iOS-web-app%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%09%09%3Cp%3E%0A%09%09%09%20%20%20%20%20%20%20Indira%20CMS%20comes%20with%20build-in%20iOS-web-app.%20You%2C%20your%20users%20and%20visitors%20may%20find%20tis%20feature%20very%20useful.%20By%20using%20web-app%20you%20will%20bring%20users-experience%20to%20real%20full%20screen%2C%20without%20navigation-bar%20and%20other%20iOS%20stuff%20like%20native%20application.%20To%20install%20application%20all%20you%20need%20is%20click%20on%20share%20icon%2C%20and%20then%20on%20%22Add%20to%20Home%20Screen%22.%20Also%20we%20bring%20%22native%20app%20scrolling%22%20into%20your%20iOS-web-app.%20And%20most%20nicely%20thing%20is%20what%20this%20feature%20is%20free%20for%20all%20your%20users%20without%20logging%20into%20App%20Store.%0A%09%09%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%09%3Ch3%3EIndira.js%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%09%3Cdiv%3E%0A%09%09%3Cp%3E%0A%09%09%09%20%20%20%20%20%20%20Script%20Indira.js%20we%20use%20to%20%22ajaxify%22%20and%20liven%20up%20our%20back-end%20and%20front-end.%20Indira.js%20will%20bring%20best%20of%20AJAX%20and%20History%20API%20to%20your%20project.%20Simply%20prepend%20to%20anchor%27s%20id%20go_to_%20or%20to%20any%20element%27s%20id%20ajax_%20and%20that%27s%20it%21%20Indira.js%20is%20fully%20controlled%20via%20data-attributes.%20We%20hope%20you%20will%20enjoy%20by%20this%20helpful%20feature.%0A%09%09%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%09%3Cdiv%3E%0A%09%09%3Ch3%3E%20SEO%20%26amp%3B%20SMM%20optimized%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%09%09%3Cp%3E%0A%09%09%09%20%20%20%20%20%20%20Each%20page%20of%20content%20generated%20by%20Indira%20CMS%20comes%20with%20all%20required%20meta-tags%20by%20search%20engines%20and%20social%20networks%20%28Open%20Graph%2C%20Twitter%29%20%2B%20extra%20blog%20%26amp%3B%20posts%20microdata%20in%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2Fhtml%2Fwg%2Fdrafts%2Fmicrodata%2Fmaster%2F%22%3EHTML5%20microdata%20specification%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Such%20as%20title%2C%20description%2C%20tags%2C%20image%2C%20icon%20and%20much%20more%2C%20all%20of%20meta-tags%20is%20editable%20via%20Templte%27s%20settings.%20By%20default%20we%20include%20Google%20Analytics%20and%20Disqus%20integration.%0A%09%09%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%09%3Chr%3E%0A%09%09%3Ch2%3EModules%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%09%09%3Cp%3E%0A%09%09%09%20%20%20%20%20%20INDIRA%20CMS%20COMES%20WITH%20ALL%20NECESSARY%20MODULES%20TO%20START%20WORK%20ON%20YOUR%20PROJECT.%0A%09%09%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%09%3Cp%3E%0A%09%09%09%20%20%20%20%20%20All%20modules%20can%20be%20turned%20on%20of%20off.%20That%20means%20-%20if%20you%20do%20not%20need%20posts%2C%20or%20blog%20module%20you%20can%20easily%20turn%20it%20off%20and%20hide%20form%20CMS%20menu.%20Functionality%20of%20all%20modules%20can%20be%20extended%20or%20minimized%20by%20your%20choice.%0A%09%09%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%09%09%09%09%3Cdiv%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%3Ch3%3EPosts%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%3Cp%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%09%20%20%20%20%20%20Posts%20is%20main%20content%20of%20your%20web-application.%20All%20posts%20is%20grouped%20by%20sections.%20By%20default%20all%20posts%20has%20QR-Code%2C%20pretty%20url%2C%20tags%2C%20Access%20Level%2C%20language%2C%20short%20description%20and%20%22related%20post%22.%20%22Related%20post%22%20allow%20to%20your%20users%20change%20current%20application%27s%20localization%20and%20read%20%22related%20post%22%20in%20choosen%20language%2C%20instantly%20by%20redirection.%20The%20%22Pretty%20URL%22%20-%20allow%20editors%20to%20set%20url%20in%20different%20languages%20for%20better%20SEO%20optimization.%3Cbr%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%09%20%20%20%20%20%20Example%20link%20to%20%22promo%22%3A%20English%20-%20domain.com%2Fpromo%2C%20Russian%20-domain.com%2F%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%BC%D0%BE%2C%20Japnese%20-%20domain.com%2F%E5%AE%A3%E4%BC%9D%E5%BA%83%E5%91%8A%20or%20Spanish%20-domain.com%2Fpromoci%C3%B3n.%20%22Pretty%20Links%22%20works%20in%20Blog%2C%20Sections%20and%20Page%20modules%20in%20same%20way.%0A%09%09%09%09%09%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%3Cdiv%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%3Ch3%3E%20Languages%20%28Localization%29%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%3Cp%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%09%20%20%20%20%20%20By%20default%20Laravel%20comes%20with%20support%20of%20Localization.%20All%20of%20the%20language%20files%20for%20your%20application%20live%20under%20the%20application%2Flanguage%20directory.%20Within%20the%20application%2Flanguage%20directory%2C%20you%20should%20create%20a%20directory%20for%20each%20language%20your%20application%20speaks.%20So%2C%20for%20example%2C%20if%20your%20application%20speaks%20English%20and%20Spanish%2C%20you%20might%20create%20en%20and%20es%20directories%20under%20the%20language%20directory.%20You%20may%20read%20full%20localization%20documantation%20at%26nbsp%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fthree.laravel.com%2Fdocs%2Flocalization%22%3ELaravel%27s%20localization%20docs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%09%20%20%20%20%20%20In%20Indira%20CMS%20we%27re%20simplify%20the%20process%20of%20using%20and%20managing%20your%20app%27s%20localizations%2C%20but%20anyways%20you%20still%20have%20to%20work%20with%20language%20files%20and%20directories%20code-editor.%0A%09%09%09%09%09%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%0A%09%09%09%09%3Cdiv%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%3Ch3%3ESections%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%3Cp%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%09%20%20%20%20%20%20Sections%20is%20used%20to%20group%20Posts%20and%20build%20tree%20of%20site-map.%20Sections%20may%20be%20nested%20and%20nesting%20depth%20has%20no%20limit.%20Sections%20is%20logically%20divided%20by%20localization.%20Each%20section%20has%20own%20and%20unique%20%22Pretty%20url%22.%0A%09%09%09%09%09%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%3C%2Fdiv%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%3Cdiv%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%3Ch3%3E%20Blog%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%3Cp%3E%0A%09%09%09%09%09%09%20%20%20%20%20%20Blog%20module%20in%20most%20cases%20is%20same%20as%20Posts%20module.%20But%20it%27s%20not%20grouped%20by%20any%20sections.%20Blog%20module